data.description: This lovely multi-level home has been well maintained. The huge driveway provides ample off-street parking for family and guests. Inside you enter into the large, bright living room. Here you have hardwood floors and a woodburning fireplace with brick hearth and nice mantle. The living room is open to the dining room. This set up is great for entertaining. Hardwood floors carry into the dining room with vaulted ceilings and glass doors to the rear yard. Beyond the dining area you have your updated kitchen with ceramic plank flooring, vaulted ceiling, and stainless-steel appliances. The white raised panel cabinetry is beautifully accented by the granite countertops and tile backsplash. The double window lets in lots of sun and overlooks the large backyard. On the upper level of the home, we have a hallway with hardwood floors and a linen closet with hardwood floors. Bedrooms 1 and 2 feature easy care laminate floors, large storage space, and ceiling fan light fixture. The hall bath feature ceramic tile floors, single bowl vanity and tub/shower with glass doors. The primary suite features easy care laminate floors, large windows, and ceiling fan light fixture. It includes a large walk-in closet and private ensuite bathroom. The ensuite features a single bowl vanity and 4 ft ceramic tile shower with glass doors.  The mid-level, below the main level, is a large study. It features LVP floors, lots of windows, and garage access. It would be a great work from home space or a playroom. Below this we have the lower level made up of a large rec room/ bedroom 4 with ceramic plank flooring and recessed lighting. The lower-level full bath features ceramic tile floors, 2 ft single bowl vanity and 3 ft ceramic tile shower with nook and stone floors. The large, partially finished laundry room features a painted concrete floor and houses your laundry machines, Trane heat pump, electric water heater, and full house humidifier. Outside the home stairs from the dining room leads to your awesome rear yard. Here you have a 13 x 9 paver patio with built-in firepit. The stone grill and bar were custom built. This area is great for outside entertaining even as the weather cools. Beyond the patio you have a huge, level, and lush yard that is fully fenced. It's ready for your pups to run and play! This home has everything you want and more. Don't let it get away - schedule your showing today!
